author: kfogel
msg: Finish issue #1687: cvs2svn can often warn instead of error.
* tools/cvs2svn/cvs2svn.py
(python version check): Use error_prefix.
(CollectData.define_tag): Just warn on invalid symbolic names, don't exit.
(Commit.commit): Don't let transcoding be a fatal error.
(main, make_path, RepositoryMirror.change_path,
RepositoryMirror.is_prunable, SymbolicNameTracker.fill_name,
SymbolicNameTracker.probe_path, SymbolicNameTracker.close_names):
Add comments indicating why exiting is appropriate, and/or fix
output format.
